## 1. Import Errors (Schemas)

### Issue
  cannot import name ‚ÄòExecutionSchema‚Äô

  ### Cause
- Class not defined or mismatched filename
- Incorrect `__init__.py` exports

### Fix
- Created `ExecutionSchema` in `schemas/execution_schema.py`
- Updated `schemas/__init__.py`
- Cleared `__pycache__`

