## 2. Package Structure Issues

### Issue
Modules not recognized (e.g., workflows, schemas)

### Cause
- Missing `__init__.py`

### Fix
- Added `__init__.py` to all packages:
  - schemas/
  - runtime/
  - workflows/
  - tools/

---

## 3. Circular Imports

### Issue
Runtime importing schemas while schemas indirectly referenced runtime

### Fix
- Enforced one-directional dependency:
  - schemas ‚Üí standalone
  - runtime ‚Üí imports schemas
  - workflows ‚Üí imports runtime

---

